                      <font color="#000000" face="arial" size="2">Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;06/17/2003&nbsp;:&nbsp; 10:34:37 PM</font>
                      &nbsp;<a href="pop_profile.asp?mode=display&id=133"><img src="images/icon_profile.gif" width="15" height="15" border="0" alt="Show Profile" title="Show Profile" align="absmiddle" hspace="6" /></a>
